Schoology,is,an,online,and,mobile,application,for,classroom,and,education,management,Schoology,offers,features,for,teachers,and,schools,to,manage,homework,and,assignments,engage,students,and,manage,education,materials,The,Schoology,API,allows,developers,to,access,and,integrate,the,functionality,of,Schoology,with,other,applications,and,to,create,new,applications,Some,example,API,methods,include,managing,comments,and,email,messages,managing,user,and,account,information,and,uploading,and,managing,documents